</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_78" id="37v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> Coler </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab>Unser frewntschaft bevor. Lieber Coler, als Bohuscho, amptman czum Totsnyck, den
                                                  <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Weiszemburger,
                                                unsern burger, für <expan>ander<ex>r</ex></expan>
                                                lewt <add>gefangen hat</add> und nicht
                                                  <expan>glaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wil, das der unser
                                                  <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> sey.
                                                  <expan>Roga<ex>mus</ex></expan>, daz du
                                                  <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, unsern
                                                  <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, <app>
<note><gap reason="illegible"/></note>
</app> gen unsern <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                                dem künig, und andern enden fürderlichen und
                                                beholffen sein wöllest, ob der
                                                  <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan>, unser
                                                  <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, ungescheczt ledig
                                                  <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> möchte. Das wöllen
                                                wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add><expan>danck<ex>en</ex></expan></add>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> iiii
                                                  <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> et
                                                  <expan>Pauli</expan>
<expan>app<ex>osto</ex>l<ex>orum</ex></expan> anno
                                                octavo. </ab></div>
</div></body>
